{"tid":205673,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"不用分那麼細，iOS 核心語言 Swift 將成 Android 發展新動力","createTime":"2017-04-18T03:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T14:58:26.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ecdaa6a7c41c04ed669ebfbead9307516899646","tid":205673,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:02:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>不用分那麼細，iOS 核心語言 Swift 將成 Android 發展新動力<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/technology/player?newsId=217839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ftechnology%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D217839&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0a86eebe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ftechnology%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D217839&h=16dbdc82\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/technology/player?newsId=217839</a></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/217839_1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F217839_1.jpeg&h=618769e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://Qooah.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FQooah.com&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=690c19e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Qooah.com</a>】無論是 iOS 或 Android 等系統，開發者的支持及取態一向是平台發展的最重要資源。近日來自意大利一所學校宣佈，即將開設全球首個開發 Android 程式的 Swift 課程。這舉動說明，現時 iOS 的核心程式語言或將成為 Android 程式的開發新動力。<br />\n<br />\n一家位於意大利以 Reggio Emilia (瑞吉歐方法) 教學的 Swift 大學，日前推出一個以 Swift 語語編寫 Android 程式的課程，目標是指導學生如何使用此程式語言作開發，同時還會配合其他平台語言作跨平台支援，從而減少當中所出現的一些限制。<br />\n<br />\n課程的核心是想透過使用定制的集成開發環境（IDE）直接開發，而不是編程轉譯，同時允許編程人員使用 Android SDK 以 Swift 代替 Java 作編程。<br />\n<br />\nApple 在 2014 年時，宣佈 iOS 系統由 Object-C 主程式語言改進至另一套新創立而且易學及執行效率可高達 2.6 倍的 Swift 語言。在發佈會當中，更加宣佈將 Swift 語言開源。消息宣佈不久，Facebook 以及 Uber 等都表示對此語言感興趣，計劃用來開發自己的產品。<br />\n<br />\n早前據 TNW 報導，Google 亦有意對 Android 的系統進行一次大換血，目的是想拋棄老舊、執行效率低而且又耗電的 Java 語言，可說是要將系統完整「砍掉重練」。至於會是那套新程式語言呢？雖然 Google 有能力像 Apple 那樣開發一套自已的程式，但分析卻指出其實 Google 有意直接採用 Apple 的 Swift 來作其中一種主要的新系統開發語言。要作出這樣大的改變難度一定是十分之巨大的，但相信以 Google 的實力絕對不是問題。<br />\n<br />\n現在，看來未來 Android 的程式開發也將會加入 Swift 行列。引用羅小豬的一句「名言」：iOS、Android 大家都是 Swift，以後就不用分得那麼細了。"},{"pid":"27cd191f4c893e8207c2144a6ccaa969a028a69d","tid":205673,"uid":23213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T17:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 始終JVM係Android 死穴"},{"pid":"6bd5087c134c0b6591f6b892d70bb35818c7f49d","tid":205673,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T17:39:49.000Z","msg":"呢個post咪討論緊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/205790/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/205790/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"29b10ffca22f94cd5f56447e903ede0dff611c4b","tid":205673,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個post咪討論緊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/205790/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/205790/page/1</a></blockquote><br />\n時光機？"},{"pid":"45a9ebe68da8b27392b3326afd71edac5e069d24","tid":205673,"uid":35542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:33:43.000Z","msg":"Google咪一早講過唔會用Swift囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BxjlT11MDW4?t=529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBxjlT11MDW4%3Ft%3D529&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0778936f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BxjlT11MDW4?t=529</a><br />\n就算好多人想Google用Kotlin,Google都未必會用<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BxjlT11MDW4?t=795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBxjlT11MDW4%3Ft%3D795&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=14ec5fc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BxjlT11MDW4?t=795</a><br />\nAndroid只會用Java架咋<br />\n<br />\n除非新OS啦,Google個新OS Fuchsia就會用自家語言Dart同Go<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/fuchsia-mirror\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Ffuchsia-mirror&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=5be1e133\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/fuchsia-mirror</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lwn.net/Articles/718267/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flwn.net%2FArticles%2F718267%2F&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e83a1c93\" target=\"_blank\">https://lwn.net/Articles/718267/</a>"},{"pid":"589a9b07cf8619a93e06240d3362525a39e6c7ea","tid":205673,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"其實Android唔係咁容易砍掉重練，太多app唔係咁易port。但係我個人其實支持Golang做Android language，而且見到Google不斷將app support加入Golang裡面，其實唔係無可能。"}]}